{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/OrbHand_logo.png?t=1739303369\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">OrbHand is a card management game where you help a wizard build his magical tower and defeat the demons, while building a beautiful village in the process. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/initial_gif.gif?t=1739303369\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game begins with a Wizard card and an Orb card. Make the Wizard ponder the Orb and start generating Mana, the most basic resource in the game. You will use it to purchase booster packs, to make new buildings and resources and to create spells.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stack your cards to create new buildings, and assign resource cards to them to create more powerful characters and spells. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make new allies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit new characters to help you produce resources, fight enemies and cast spells. Each one has it's own unique capabilities! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cast spells and fight enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/combat_gif_dragon.gif?t=1739303369\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Produce and cast spell cards that can greatly impact the gameboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight goblins, elves and other creatures that invade your town. Defeat five bosses and survive the last encounter against the Demon hordes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Characteristics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83c\udccf Drag and drop cards to stack and assign them \ud83c\udccf</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83e\uddd9\u200d\u2642\ufe0f Make allies and fight evil cards \ud83e\uddd9\u200d\u2642\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \u26a1 Create and cast spells \u26a1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f Make new buildings \ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83d\udd0e Unlock recipes \ud83d\udd0d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83d\udcb0 Complete objectives to receive rewards \ud83d\udcb0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83c\udfef Build the Tower \ud83c\udfef</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83d\ude08 Defeat the Demons! \ud83d\ude08</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739303369","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739303369","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/4fe276ab0642ec1a1f65fc2b8811a4dc6abdfeab/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739303369","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/4fe276ab0642ec1a1f65fc2b8811a4dc6abdfeab/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739303369","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3387130,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/OrbHand_logo.png?t=1739303369\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">OrbHand is a card management game where you help a wizard build his magical tower and defeat the demons, while building a beautiful village in the process. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/initial_gif.gif?t=1739303369\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game begins with a Wizard card and an Orb card. Make the Wizard ponder the Orb and start generating Mana, the most basic resource in the game. You will use it to purchase booster packs, to make new buildings and resources and to create spells.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stack your cards to create new buildings, and assign resource cards to them to create more powerful characters and spells. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make new allies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit new characters to help you produce resources, fight enemies and cast spells. Each one has it's own unique capabilities! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cast spells and fight enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/combat_gif_dragon.gif?t=1739303369\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Produce and cast spell cards that can greatly impact the gameboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight goblins, elves and other creatures that invade your town. Defeat five bosses and survive the last encounter against the Demon hordes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Characteristics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83c\udccf Drag and drop cards to stack and assign them \ud83c\udccf</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83e\uddd9\u200d\u2642\ufe0f Make allies and fight evil cards \ud83e\uddd9\u200d\u2642\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \u26a1 Create and cast spells \u26a1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f Make new buildings \ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83d\udd0e Unlock recipes \ud83d\udd0d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83d\udcb0 Complete objectives to receive rewards \ud83d\udcb0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83c\udfef Build the Tower \ud83c\udfef</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- \ud83d\ude08 Defeat the Demons! \ud83d\ude08</p>","developers":["Jesus Rugarcia"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/212